text:
A plane carrying a medical evacuation team was sent to a remote Alaskan community to save a child's life but found the runway's lights had failed.

In 20 minutes, dozens of residents assembled cars and 4-wheelers to light the way so the plane could land. https://t.co/9hJHh6YOXJ
